{"tid":1685701,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[自創招式]教你如何推post上熱門","createTime":"2019-10-31T16:38:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T01:27:05.000Z","uid":158804,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"aee29e413fb056c0378cd66bc6341b5e48c12c43","tid":1685701,"uid":158804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T16:38:16.000Z","msg":"經常見到有巴絲話行動post上唔到熱門，或者上一陣就會唔見咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我做online相關工作，有少少意見想講<br />\n推測想上熱門唔單止要有人推post，而係會計有幾多人click入去、逗留時間長短等等<br />\n舉個例，前幾日有個sex post講啪啪啪暗號上熱門，但唔算太多人覆&amp;正皮，再推測係因為好撚多咸濕巴絲追post，所以好快就上到熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講咁多，咁有咩方法可以推重要post上熱門呢<br />\n第一當然要大家幫手瘋狂推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其次係行動post除行動相關資訊，其實可以加插其他可讀性高內容，去增加逗留係post嘅時間<br />\n例如亂世中有咩書單推介之類，無關痛癢但最好有益嘅內容都得<br />\n另外就係連登仔經常做嘅標題黨，其實好有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上都係我嘅推測，希望大家可以合力推有用/行動post，唔好比5毛亂連登<br />\n<br />\n最後，光復香港 時代革命<br />\n11月2日見<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eqM7T1q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeqM7T1q.jpg&h=7c707bb1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f571b54259a559aa15a6b1b26ec38427cee22c22","tid":1685701,"uid":158804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T16:39:27.000Z","msg":"自推+實測<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"150ddaf2dfcf032608e5180df94b2bc77ce2a72f","tid":1685701,"uid":314509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T16:40:01.000Z","msg":"小妹P牌 推唔郁攬炒巴個最新rundown點算好<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji